revir, Sulfadiazine, Lactic acid, Mitapivat, Methazolamide, Darunavir, Probenecid, Tioconazole, Brinzolamide, More', 'Methotrimeprazine, Quetiapine, Asenapine, Thiothixene, Pimavanserin, Lumateperone, Clozapine, Olanzapine, Aripiprazole, Loxapine, Molindone, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/238661/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767369485);
